field_key.program_name: String. Marketing name of the program/league as displayed.
field_key.venue_name: String. Name of the venue where games are played.
field_key.venue_map_url: URL. Google Maps link to the venue/location.
field_key.timing_raw: String. Raw timing line from the card (e.g., 'Oct 11 • 6 Weeks • 09:00 AM - 12:00 PM').
field_key.start_date_text: String. Start date text parsed from timing_raw (Month Day, no year).
field_key.weeks: Integer. Number of scheduled weeks parsed from timing_raw.
field_key.time_start: String. Start time in 12-hour format parsed from timing_raw.
field_key.time_end: String. End time in 12-hour format parsed from timing_raw.
field_key.skill_levels: Array<String>. Ordered list of skill-level tags (e.g., ['Upper Intermediate','Recreational']).
field_key.features: Array<String>. Venue/league feature badges (tooltip values), deduplicated.
field_key.banner_message: String. Optional promotional banner message (e.g., 'Value Turf League').
field_key.registration_phase_text: String. Phase line, typically 'Registration Ends MM/DD'.
field_key.registration_ends_mmdd: String. Parsed end date (MM/DD) from registration_phase_text when present.
field_key.price_person_base: Number. Base/original per-person price (USD) if shown.
field_key.member_price_original: Number. Original per-person price shown under 'Membership Pricing' (USD).
field_key.image_alt: String. Alt text describing the sport/format.
field_key.perks_more_url: URL. Link to a details page listing all perks/features.
